docs {
  ## List Vendors
  แสดงรายการผู้ขายทั้งหมดพร้อมการแบ่งหน้าและค้นหา

  Retrieves all vendors/suppliers configured in the business unit with pagination and search support.

  ### Path Parameters
  | Name | Type | Description |
  |------|------|-------------|
  | `bu_code` | string | Business unit code |

  ### Query Parameters
  | Name | Type | Description |
  |------|------|-------------|
  | `version` | string | API version (default: latest) |

  ### Headers
  | Name | Required | Description |
  |------|----------|-------------|
  | `Authorization` | Yes | `Bearer {{access_token}}` |
  | `x-app-id` | Yes | `{{x_app_id}}` |

  ### Permissions
  - **Permission key**: `vendor_management.vendor:view`
  - **Roles**: Requestor, HOD, Purchase, Approval

  ### Sample Response
  ```json
  {
    "data": [
      {
        "id": "019638a6-2a00-7c4f-8e46-9b7a52c80c4d",
        "code": "VND-2024-0001",
        "name": "Siam Fresh Co., Ltd.",
        "description": "Fresh produce and food ingredients supplier",
        "is_active": true,
        "created_at": "2026-04-29T08:30:00.000Z"
      }
    ],
    "paginate": {
      "total": 50,
      "page": 1,
      "perpage": 10,
      "pages": 5
    },
    "status": 200,
    "success": true,
    "message": "Success",
    "timestamp": "2026-04-29T08:30:00.000Z"
  }
  ```

  ### Error Responses
  | Status | When |
  |--------|------|
  | 401 | Missing or invalid bearer token |
  | 403 | User lacks `vendor_management.vendor:view` permission |
}
